                    </div>
                    <span>This is an excellent book. One of the best I have ever read in my life. While you read it you get so many ideas about life, research, people...For me, as a doctoral student making a thesis on  multicriterion optimization, it is a revelation.
<br />I highly recommend it to everyone, since it is not a technical book, but written with ease for a layman. For the people in the business of decision making, I bet that you will be amazed with the impressions you get from it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Very good for the common reader</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
